data.name: tsbEquipment.ToolTipText
data.value:
Foothold ---------- Allows you to create anchor points that map out a physical shape.
Only map out what the player should stand on.
e.g A box only needs a connection between its two top corners.
This is only available when interacting with foreground layers (0 - 7).
